{"tid":1566641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行完獅子山  我反省","createTime":"2019-09-13T16:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T22:13:03.000Z","uid":298038,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2a176d6d42eba4133911109254193d1f03281c04","tid":1566641,"uid":298038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我知我P牌</span><br />\n<br />\n先講結論<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">以後遊行真係唔好再嘉年華</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n行完913獅子山  無可否認既係<br />\n我地整體真係<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬆懈</span></ins>左<br />\n我今日玩得好開心  笑9肥媽首歌  係度高音啊啊啊<br />\n但係行完之後  我回想我到底做左d咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">預先慶功???場仗仲有排打喎!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n我明白  要守不分化原則<br />\n但方向歪左真係要提點<br />\n外國人見到我地係度肥媽嘉年華  就會覺得香港人不外如是<br />\n兒戲嘉年華 &lt; 仇恨敵人 &lt; 圍爐凝聚 &lt; 為民求變革<br />\n肥媽歌 &lt; 有班警察 &lt; 國歌榮光 &lt; 和勇合一的各種行動<br />\n<br />\n我明白美國國會通過法案既機會唔細<br />\n作為香港人  我心底裡覺得真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黎明來到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n正因為咁  心開始怠倦<br />\n開始覺得  美國會幫我地搞架啦<br />\n等佢地開會啦  會過架啦<br />\n<br />\n但其實除左等  我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有好多野要做  唔好停</span></span><br />\n美國以外  歐盟戰線都要人<br />\n就算過左法案  中共既文攻武鬥  一定唔會停<br />\n佢地有大把爛仔  大把奴才可以徵用<br />\n沒有最廢  只有更廢<br />\n場仗仲有排打<br />\n<br />\n幫推post<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去戰線幫手出力啦!!</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1566358/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1566358/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連儂牆文宣</span>呢  各位要組織一隊人去補牆<br />\n落單補牆小心被襲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港  時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"5d9ec2e75d4598ad3424efc23f48e6b6e76aefd1","tid":1566641,"uid":179873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n玩還玩，唔好玩上腦"},{"pid":"16c4a23ebaa9f9780f1ef2e37ae71d74ae498571","tid":1566641,"uid":227776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"講得幾啱，大家今日當休息下，聽日要繼續加油"},{"pid":"88d54f729f737075f1a1e9c87eb5b1df7060949f","tid":1566641,"uid":137265,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"呢幾日當係比和理非提升翻參與度<br />\n希望大家915會出黎"},{"pid":"4f257b71188b60787aedf8d7c9e0a6056b18fd79","tid":1566641,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"推 休息為了走更遠的路<br />\n各位巴絲即刻收拾心情 所有戰線火力全開"},{"pid":"8c3d612577cb6d2b9d898ce154a1b4aa33e3d3a7","tid":1566641,"uid":160262,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"行獅子山唔算係遊行<br />\n同埋根本行唔到<br />\n中秋就算啦<br />\n幾多人 唔同屋企人過 都想出嚟同大家過<br />\n<br />\n915遊行 就唔好鬆懈啦"},{"pid":"ce2f5dc2ff9e6aa5cf3010cbcb9208beedc279eb","tid":1566641,"uid":277595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7308b63b3f2a42d0681fde64c38420875fa89a0a","tid":1566641,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"講左半個月，就算通過左都唔會對現狀有咩大改變，一樣恐將分子干政，殺人強姦日日做<br />\n<br />\n而家過到未過己經成班日日開嘉年華，有時真心覺得香港人抵而撚死，日後好好係集中營度後悔自己on9白白錯失百年一遇既獨立富多時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c298537c05943178eae4359f69149e067fd3415","tid":1566641,"uid":141056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:50:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0aa3190bd7396ade1ed6ed13a888739adc27d08b","tid":1566641,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad016a8e749acc4b65785146183c11d7824fe2c","tid":1566641,"uid":306180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"[red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叉夠電，港島見！</span>[/red<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nr0tUy3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnr0tUy3.jpg&h=9afddcd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1212207345f788f7682fe261d8f844bae454d8a9","tid":1566641,"uid":192836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"中秋一齊過節 幾個鐘輕鬆就由佢好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一落山同平時出返嚟示威 會依然勇武"},{"pid":"3007430bee015fc50455f1aaeee6b9da3c14c46a","tid":1566641,"uid":129848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7308b63b3f2a42d0681fde64c38420875fa89a0a","tid":1566641,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"講左半個月，就算通過左都唔會對現狀有咩大改變，一樣恐將分子干政，殺人強姦日日做<br />\n<br />\n而家過到未過己經成班日日開嘉年華，有時真心覺得香港人抵而撚死，日後好好係集中營度後悔自己on9白白錯失百年一遇既獨立富多時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"吊頸都要透氣啦大佬 人地真係打仗嘅士兵都要放break 更何況香港人3個月除咗尖沙咀撚筆嗰次之外乜開心嘢都冇發生過？ 如果915變成嘉年華嘅話我幫你屌埋一份 但係依一刻唔放鬆一下真係會痴線㗎 <br />\n香港咁多年都冇類似國歌嘅凝聚民心樂曲 6日內已經揚遍18區你竟然睇唔出香港人真正「獨立」identity覺醒而喺度心灰？"},{"pid":"a427839f3a8a450907df35c0888b260f60ec903b","tid":1566641,"uid":243588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n玩係冇問題<br />\n只不過係提醒翻香港人玩完就要收拾心情姐<br />\n吊頸都要抖下氣啦<br />\n加油香港人！"},{"pid":"a429a7c5b55471892e93b0ba24fc8435e1a84c9a","tid":1566641,"uid":154187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:26:51.000Z","msg":"中秋節放鬆下一晚都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55407aa7aecab8235f1ef32026effafdf9cb413c","tid":1566641,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:03:04.000Z","msg":"推 繼續加油"},{"pid":"4065a9a6b41600b1559d766034b7492d39d902d6","tid":1566641,"uid":267964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7b2c4fbed72f207654454afdac96ad4a86d22c3","tid":1566641,"uid":293487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我反省<br />\n今日大家輕鬆一次，然後繼續努力打場仗！<br />\n橡筋chur得太緊會斷嫁，放返鬆少少先啦香港人。 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228d0b8bc77a77e5ca2ec44e2b4a2740264f66c5","tid":1566641,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T21:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a039eea4a060a00c84d24f431a5f72770ed4cff","tid":1566641,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T21:48:16.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"c4abe1471d498bdcad7df0a890da928b733c9178","tid":1566641,"uid":178684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T21:50:27.000Z","msg":"吊頸都要抖氣"},{"pid":"a4e06143dde710b1186597a63451a13ef1c613f3","tid":1566641,"uid":295353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:13:03.000Z","msg":"真係好怕大家都會繼續沉迷於呢啲嘉年華，美國人權法嗰邊其實都幾危險，中共有大把黑金用嚟收䍚啲國會議員，你估真係個個都真係擁護國家利益同埋人權自由咩，又有幾多人真係可以做到完全不受金錢動搖，尤其係香港呢一個影響唔到佢哋自身利益嘅問題，點解要為咗我哋而向呢一大堆錢say no呢？<br />\n我知我嘅想法好負面，但係我真係好驚會有一大堆原本支持法案嘅國會議員轉軚，然後其他都開始表態反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，大家玩埋今次就要focus翻成個抗爭嘅目的<br />\n勿忘初心啊咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果呢條法例過唔到嘅話可能香港真係會變咗做第二個新彊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}